---
title: Red Thai Style Udon Noodle Soup with Pak Choi and Mushrooms
description: This delicious Red Thai Style Udon Noodle Soup has been expertly designed by our chefs as a lighter option to help with a balanced lifestyle.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R23_W17_UK_V20250-4_Main_low-29e277e3.jpg
